another link : https://practice.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/reversal-algorithm5340/1?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=collab_striver_ytdescription&utm_campaign=reversal-algorithm

optimize solution : You can use different language and if there is no reverse function then you can create reverse function.

class Solution{   
public:
    void leftRotate(int arr[], int n, int d) {
        // code here
        reverse(arr, arr+d);
        reverse(arr+d, arr+n);
        reverse(arr, arr+n);
        
    }
